 Neurologi\u0301a Afectiva) y su influencia sobre el comportamiento del consumidor.\nLoading Preview\nSorry, preview is currently unavailable. You can download the paper by clicking the button above.\nDiscusiones contempor\u00e1neas en filosof\u00eda de la mente. Voces locales\n2019 \u2022\nLa segunda persona y las emociones\n2017 \u2022\nNeurociencia Afectiva - Jorge Ure\n2019 \u2022", "language": null, "image": "http://a.academia-assets.com/images/open-graph-icons/fb-book.gif", "pagetype": "book", "links": ["https://www.academia.edu/privacy", "https://www.academia.edu/upgrade-browser", "javascript:void(0)", "https://www.academia.edu/signup", "https://www.academia.edu/", "https://www.academia.edu/login", "https://www.academia.edu/signup", "https://www.academia.edu/login", "https://www.academia.edu/signup", "https://www.academia.edu/Jobs", "https://www.academia.edu/about", "https://www.academia.edu/press", "https://medium.com/@academia", "https://www.academia.edu/Directory/People", "https://www.academia.edu/Directory/Papers", "https://www.academia.edu/terms", "https://www.academia.edu/privacy", "https://www.academia.edu/copyright", "https://www.academia.edu/hiring", "https://support.academia.edu/", "https://www.academia.edu/attachments/60683288/download_file?st=MTY5NTQzODkyNSwyMTcuMjM4LjEzMS4yNDY%3D&s=swp-splash-paper-cover", "https://uba.academia.edu/RebecaStein", "https://www.academia.edu/11326305/La_Emocio_n_y_los_Marcadores_Soma_ticos_Un_Modelo_de_Decisio_n_de_Compra", "https://independent.academia.edu/CristinaAlc%C3%A2ntara", "https://www.academia.edu/11326305/La_Emocio_n_y_los_Marcadores_Soma_ticos_Un_Modelo_de_Decisio_n_de_Compra", "https://www.academia.edu/32950272/Cuadernos_de_Mente_y_cerebro_n_o", "https://independent.academia.edu/CarmenJackson2", "https://www.academia.edu/32950272/Cuadernos_de_Mente_y_cerebro_n_o", "https://www.academia.edu/12569642/Cuadernos_de_Mente_y_cerebro_n_o_2", "https://independent.academia.edu/NatiMataveri", "https://www.academia